</para></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="rc-gui-mini-set-lyric-persent" role="function">
<title>rc_gui_mini_set_lyric_persent ()</title>
<indexterm zone="rc-gui-mini-set-lyric-persent"><primary>rc_gui_mini_set_lyric_persent</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting><link linkend="void"><returnvalue>void</returnvalue></link>                rc_gui_mini_set_lyric_persent       (<parameter><link linkend="gdouble"><type>gdouble</type></link> persent</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>
Make the view of the lyric label move by given persent if the lyric text
is too loog.
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>persent</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara>the persent position of the lyric text
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
<refsect2 id="rc-gui-mini-set-play-state" role="function">
<title>rc_gui_mini_set_play_state ()</title>
<indexterm zone="rc-gui-mini-set-play-state"><primary>rc_gui_mini_set_play_state</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting><link linkend="void"><returnvalue>void</returnvalue></link>                rc_gui_mini_set_play_state          (<parameter><link linkend="gboolean"><type>gboolean</type></link> state</parameter>);</programlisting>
<para>
Set play button state.
</para><variablelist role="params">
<varlistentry><term><parameter>state</parameter>&#160;:</term>
<listitem><simpara>the state of the play button, if it's TRUE, the image of the
button is pause icon, else the image is play icon.
</simpara></listitem></varlistentry>
</variablelist></refsect2>
